metadata.description: 258 powerful Crystals on the Ethereum blockchain from Earth that has been infused with the unlimited energy of the non-terrestrial Core Crystal that was recently unearthed. Scarcely produced for our most early supporters, each Keeper NFT is handcrafted to be a unique piece, non-generative. Designed for holders (Keepers), each gem is infused with Forever Utilities, and acts as a board member badge to determine the story-telling concept of D.A.F.T.
metadata.name: Keeper #1
